\begin{align*}
6&>g\\
25&>g^2\\
25&>4a\\
a&<\frac{25}{4}\\
\end{align*}
In summary, we have\begin{align*}
a&>27\\
a&<\frac{25}{4}
\end{align*}
Of the integer values between $27$ and $\frac{25}{4}$ exclusive, is 
